Kerala's name has not officially been changed. The cited source was a non-binding resolution by the Kerala Legislative Assembly. State Name Changes in the Republic of India cannot occur without assent and permission by the Indian Federal Government, which it has not given yet. Therefore, Kerala remains Kerala, contrary to the contents of this page presumably edited prematurely.
